'''斯蒂芬·科拜尔晚间秀'''（{{lang-en|''The Late Show with Stephen Colbert''}}，[[BLUE_ANT_Entertainment|Big Ant娛樂台]]译名：荷-{伯}-報到）是[[斯蒂芬·科拜尔|斯蒂芬·科拜尔]]在[[CBS|CBS]]频道所主持的深夜[[脱口秀|脱口秀]]节目，这是CBS该著名脱口秀[[晚间秀|晚间秀]]第二次主持迭代。节目于2015年9月在晚间秀''Late Show''主持[[大卫·莱特曼|大卫·莱特曼]]<ref>{{cite news|title=<nowiki>Stephen Colbert Named New ‘Late Show’ Host</nowiki>|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/stephen-colbert-new-late-show-host-replacing-david-letterman/|accessdate=2014-04-10|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2014-04-10|archive-date=2014-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411221933/http://www.deadline.com/2014/04/stephen-colbert-new-late-show-host-replacing-david-letterman/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>C{{cite news |first=Bill |last=Carter |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |title=David Letterman to Retire in 2015 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/04/business/media/david-letterman-to-retire-in-2015.html |date=2014-04-03 |accessdate=2014-04-03 |archive-date=2014-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140403213012/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/04/business/media/david-letterman-to-retire-in-2015.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>退休后播出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/279723272.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-12-16 |archive-date=2015-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108010331/http://www.startribune.com/entertainment/279723272.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==历史==
[[File:Stephen_Colbert_and_Steve_Carell_MFF_2014_(cropped).jpg|left]]自从2005年10月主持自己的节目以来已获得了四个[[艾米奖|艾米奖]]项]]
CBS曾经制作过脱口秀''[[The_Merv_Griffin_Show|The Merv Griffin Show]]''（1969–1972）和''[[The_Pat_Sajak_Show|The Pat Sajak Show]]''（1989–1990）但都无法与[[NBC|NBC]]旗下的约翰尼·卡森所今夜秀抗衡，而两个节目最终都因极低的用户评价而被取消。晚间秀初创之时CBS旗下晚间节目包括电影、重播及特别制作的节目都以''[[The_CBS_Late_Movie|CBS Late Night]]''和''[[Crimetime_After_Primetime|Crimetime After Primetime]]''为题在黄金时段后播出。莱特曼曾为NBC节目《深夜秀》（Late Night）的主持人，而他一直也被外界视为《[[今夜秀|今夜秀]]》（Tonight Show）主持人约翰尼·卡森的接班人。但在约翰尼·卡森准备退休之际，NBC决定将《今夜秀》主持人一职交予杰伊·里诺（Jay Leno）。此举令莱特曼十分气愤及失望，CBS在此之际用一个为期三年，相当于莱特曼之前收入两倍约每年1400万美金的合約吸引其加入了CBS<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,305416,00.html |title=Is Dave Worth It? |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |first=Mark |last=Harris |date=1993-01-29 |accessdate=2011-12-07 |archive-date=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113042850/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,305416,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

从1993年以来莱特曼的''晚间秀''取得了巨大的成功，初始两年收视率即超越了NBC旗下的''今夜秀''。在2013年2月，晚间秀约有平均310万的集收视率。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/02/14/late-night-tv-ratings-for-february-4-8-2013/169497/ |title=Late Night TV Ratings For February 4-8, 2013 |publisher=zap2it.com |date=2013-02-14 |accessdate=2013-09-14 |quote=<nowiki>Season-to-date figures are averages of “live plus seven day” data except for the two most recent weeks, which are “live plus same day.”)... SEASON TO DATE/TOTAL VIEWERS...11:35 p.m.-12:35 a.m. ET: NBC “Tonight,” 3.6 million viewers, CBS “Late Show,” 3.1 million viewers, ABC “Kimmel,”</nowiki> 2.8 million viewers** |archive-date=2015-05-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150531114044/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/02/14/late-night-tv-ratings-for-february-4-8-2013/169497/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>但2014年统计，收视率降到了280万。<ref name="AdAge2014"/> 在深夜脱口秀中晚间秀的观众群体平均年龄最老，这导致了CBS决心选择一个年轻的替代者以和NBC旗下的[[今夜秀|今夜秀]]竞争。<ref name= "AdAge2014">{{cite news |first=Jeanine |last=Poggi |work=[[Advertising_Age|Advertising Age]] |title=Why Jimmy Fallon's 'Tonight Show' Can Thrive With Fewer Viewers When Conan's Couldn't |url=http://adage.com/article/media/jimmy-fallon-s-tonight-show-thrive-fewer-viewers/291646/ |date=2014-02-13 |accessdate=2014-02-14 |archive-date=2014-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214094755/http://adage.com/article/media/jimmy-fallon-s-tonight-show-thrive-fewer-viewers/291646/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年4月3日，莱特曼宣布将在2015年退休，[[斯蒂芬·科拜尔|斯蒂芬·科拜尔]]同意了为期五年的合同并将在2015年从莱特曼手中接任主持位置。科拜尔以前的节目在在深夜喜剧节目主要受众大学生和青年中很受欢迎。<ref name="AdAge2014"/>在科拜尔之前主持的节目[[科拜尔报告|科拜尔报告]]中，其扮演的虚构人物也叫[[斯蒂芬·科拜尔_(角色)|斯蒂芬·科拜尔]]，科拜尔将举办展会以和自己本人进行对比。<ref>{{cite news |last=Pergament |first=Alan |date=2014-04-10 |url=http://blogs.buffalonews.com/talkintv/2014/04/choice-of-colbert-to-succeed-letterman-makes-perfect-sense-.html |title=Choice of Colbert to succeed Letterman makes perfect sense |newspaper=The Buffalo News |accessdate=2014-04-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412195258/http://blogs.buffalonews.com/talkintv/2014/04/choice-of-colbert-to-succeed-letterman-makes-perfect-sense-.html |archivedate=2014年4月12日 }}</ref>2014年4月23日，虚构的斯蒂芬·科拜尔在乔恩斯图尔特[[每日秀|每日秀]]上宣布他已“赢得电视（won television）”，因为自己达到了目标，所以他将会终止科拜尔报告。在接过莱特曼的节目后科拜尔将不会再以虚构人物斯蒂芬·科拜尔的立场出现。<ref>{{cite news |first=Esther |last=Zuckerman |work=The Wire |title=Stephen Colbert Will Take Over for David Letterman |url=http://www.thewire.com/entertainment/2014/04/stephen-colbert-will-take-over-for-david-letterman/360481/ |date=2014-04-10 |accessdate=2014-07-23 |archive-date=2014-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815113922/http://www.thewire.com/entertainment/2014/04/stephen-colbert-will-take-over-for-david-letterman/360481/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

包括[[纽约市|纽约市]]，[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]，[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]和[[康涅狄格|康涅狄格]]都希望让晚间秀在其城市举行。<ref>{{cite news |last=Hutchins |first=Ryan |date=2014-04-11 |url=http://www.capitalnewyork.com/article/media/2014/04/8543581/battle-colberts-late-show |title=The battle for Colbert's 'Late Show' |work=Capital New York |accessdate=2014-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413051332/http://www.capitalnewyork.com/article/media/2014/04/8543581/battle-colberts-late-show |archive-date=2014-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2014年7月23日，CBS宣布晚间秀在科拜尔接管后还将继续在纽约埃德·苏利文剧院举行。<ref name=hr>{{cite news|title=Stephen Colbert's 'Late Show' to Stay at Ed Sullivan Theatre|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/stephen-colberts-late-show-stay-720643|accessdate=2014-07-24|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-07-23|archive-date=2014-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140725182634/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/stephen-colberts-late-show-stay-720643|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年6月4日，CBS宣布乐队指挥为乔纳森·巴蒂斯特，他和其乐队Stay Human将担任科拜尔晚间秀的室内乐队。（該樂隊亦繼承原[[大卫·莱特曼晚间秀|大卫·莱特曼晚间秀]]伴奏樂隊{{Link-en|保羅·沙佛和世上最危險樂隊|Paul Shaffer and the World's Most Dangerous Band}}節目停播後不再使用的「{{Link-en|CBS乐队|CBS Orchestra}}」名稱）<ref name=human>{{cite news|title=Indiana musician makes late night TV cast|url=https://www.indianagazette.com/news/indiana-news/indiana-musician-makes-late-night-tv-cast,50009753/|accessdate=2015-06-07|work=Indiana Gazette|date=2015-06-05|archive-date=2016-01-18|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160118174052/https://www.indianagazette.com/news/indiana-news/indiana-musician-makes-late-night-tv-cast,50009753/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Meet Stephen Colbert’s New Late Show Bandleader, Jon Batiste|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/06/stephen-colbert-jon-batiste-late-show|accessdate=2015-06-07|work=Vanity Fair|date=2015-06-06|archive-date=2015-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150607104511/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2015/06/stephen-colbert-jon-batiste-late-show|dead-url=no}}</ref>

